{"tid":1100270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「高等華人社會系列」鄭汝樺：民望上升是鼓勵","createTime":"2019-04-10T09:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:49:52.000Z","uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b1f0cd2d46fda097eccb7283a845aa96dbf5c94","tid":1100270,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:47:31.000Z","msg":"文章日期：2010年1月14日<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】立法會財務委員會明日再次審議高鐵撥款，運輸及房屋局長鄭汝樺昨趁立法會大會的機會，逗留立法會前廳約5小時，盡最後努力游說議員支持撥款及不要拉布拖延。她昨首次回應高鐵爭議下其民望不跌反升，她指這對她和高鐵支持者是一種鼓勵，證明許多人認同此項目是為了社會長遠利益，但現階段政府有責任再作耐心解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20100114/s00012/d9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20100114%2Fs00012%2Fd9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg&h=165a82e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20100114/s00012/d9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20100114%2Fs00012%2Fd9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg&h=165a82e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20100114/s00012/d9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20100114%2Fs00012%2Fd9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg&h=165a82e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cbc452f04adcc969d38b37e04b8543f61db555a","tid":1100270,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T09:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs1.mingpao.com/education/20100114/s00012/d9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs1.mingpao.com%2Feducation%2F20100114%2Fs00012%2Fd9df449f09258f517bd42ed742a1384f.jpg&h=165a82e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錢而袋理底線得你"}]}